{"tid":2374931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇 伊藤英明日本有主角唔做 走去美國做一個一句對白都冇既拆牆佬？","createTime":"2021-01-21T15:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T06:16:42.000Z","uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4a5c19a148897f93ace26facc54426fc0ac94744","tid":2374931,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnO6S3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnO6S3g.jpg&h=490eb210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇緊Doorman 睇左頭15分鐘已經覺得係爛片<br />\n點知冇啦啦彈左個亞洲樣拆牆賊出來<br />\n（香港rocky咁既角色）<br />\n唔洗講對白 一味傻笑<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味咁熟口面既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n停左睇多兩秒 伊藤英明來既喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwFAMny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwFAMny.jpg&h=b68c75fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXiR4ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXiR4ae.jpg&h=33b88331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（後邊個位rocky就係啦）<br />\n<br />\n依家重睇緊 睇了一半<br />\n伊藤英明未講過野 出場負責傻笑同拆牆<br />\n我成套戲變左專注落佢到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n佢弱智 有主角唔做去做茄喱啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人各有志 能屈能伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bbe2f3d45b8cdb7af651498ad7ffba6e39ec2d","tid":2374931,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe53f5eb2d2b5f5760422fc8d911036b69297f4","tid":2374931,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20